Subject: [PATCH 14/14] arm64: dts: rk3588-orangepi-5-plus: Add dwc3 reset
 quirk

This is needed to apply type-c muxing/orientation properly to the phy.

Signed-off-by: Ondrej Jirman <megi@xff.cz>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/rockchip/rk3588-orangepi-5-plus.dts | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/rockchip/rk3588-orangepi-5-plus.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/rockchip/rk3588-orangepi-5-plus.dts
index e4b3ff8f0bc5..615830645925 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/rockchip/rk3588-orangepi-5-plus.dts
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/rockchip/rk3588-orangepi-5-plus.dts
@@ -405,6 +405,7 @@ usbdp_phy0_typec_sbu: endpoint@1 {
 
 &usb_host0_xhci {
 	usb-role-switch;
+	snps,usb3-phy-reset-quirk;
 
 	port {
 		usb_host0_xhci_drd_sw: endpoint {
